OL,5, A man who lived in a supermarket car   
OL,6, park for five years has said winter    
OL,7, shelter pods being offered to rough    
OL,8, sleepers have given him "hope".        
OL,10,FTen self-contained pods provide        
OL,11,Femergency housing in Blackburn for     
OL,12,Fthose who have nowhere else to go.     
OL,14,FThe idea came during the Covid-19      
OL,15,Fpandemic when the government provided  
OL,16,Ffunding to local authorities to        
OL,17,Faccommodate homeless people.           
OL,19,FCharlie said: "If it wasn't for this   
OL,20,Fplace, I'd be living in a car."        
